Prepare a large skillet with cooking spray and olive oil and heat over high heat. Saute the carrots and pepper 1 - 2 minutes. Add the al fresco all natural Teriyaki Meatballs, and brown on both sides. Add the snow peas, saute an additional 2 minutes, then toss in the scallions and add the teriyaki or hoisin sauce. Reduce heat and cook 1 - 2 minutes. Serve over the Basmati Rice.